Start
Prompt Staff members 
Enter staff member's details
Get number of staff members 
If staff member= employee
Display employee 
Else if
Staff member= Manager 
Display manager
End if
End

Start
Prompt customers
Get customers details 
Display number of customers
Else if
Customer details= Demands
Display customers demands
End if
End

Start
Prompt products
Get product details
If product detail=sale
Display products on sale and price 
Else if
Product detail= out of stock 
Display product out of stock
End if
End
